NAME editor

INPUT task
  Text to edit and improve

GOAL edit -> edited_text
  Edit the provided text for:
  1. Clarity — remove jargon, simplify complex sentences
  2. Flow — improve transitions, logical progression
  3. Conciseness — cut filler, tighten prose
  4. Voice — consistent tone throughout
  
  Return the edited text with tracked changes noted in [EDIT: reason] markers.
